 floor-length shawls worn by Southern Afghan men, a
 s well as table linen, women’s head-coverings, and gi
 rls’ wedding trousseaus. WORKS OF HONOR , LOVE Traditional Khamak includes natural themes, such as flowers, leaves and trees, in addition to the geometric shapes of Islamic art." />


            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:textSize="32dp"
                android:text="Estimated Population"

                />
            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:textSize="22dp"
                android:text="614,118 (2020)"
                />


            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:textSize="32dp"
                android:text="Famous Places"

                />
            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:textSize="18dp"
                android:text="Mausoleum of Ahmad Shah Durran , Arghandab River"
                />
            <GridLayout
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="fill_parent"
                android:rowCount="4"
                android:rowOrderPreserved="true"
                android:columnCount="1"
                android:layout_gravity="center">

                <ImageView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="250dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/k1"
                    android:layout_marginTop="1dp"
                    android:layout_marginBottom="100px">

                </ImageView>


                <ImageView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="250dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/k"


                    android:layout_marginBottom="100px">
                </ImageView>


                <ImageView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="250dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/k3"
                    android:layout_marginBottom="100px">
                </ImageView>





                <ImageView
